@startuml MatchMonitorClassification_SP_GetMatches
title CTS_DC_CustClassification_MatchMonitor_Get - Detailed Flow

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FFE0B2
skinparam activityBorderColor #F57C00
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam noteBorderColor #FBC02D

start
:SP: **CTS_DC_CustClassification_MatchMonitor_Get**;
note right
  **Database**: CTS_DataCenter.ctsServiceAdmin
  **Purpose**: Get list of matches needing status update
  **Called by**: UpdateStatusMatchMonitor Job
  **Return Type**: List<int> (MatchIDs)
end note

:Execute Query;
note right
  **Query Logic**:
  ```sql
  SELECT DISTINCT MatchID
  FROM CTSMatchMonitor
  WHERE 1=1
    -- Get unfinished matches
    AND (EventStatus IS NULL 
         OR EventStatus NOT IN ('Closed', 'Finished'))
    
    -- Not yet completed
    AND IsCompleted = 0
    
    -- Has associated details
    AND EXISTS (
      SELECT 1 
      FROM CTSMatchMonitorDetail d
      WHERE d.MatchID = CTSMatchMonitor.MatchID
    )
  
  ORDER BY MatchID ASC
  ```
  
  **Filters**:
  - Unfinished matches (not Closed/Finished)
  - Not completed (IsCompleted = 0)
  - Has detection details
  
  **Purpose**:
  - Get matches needing status sync
  - Maintain accurate EventStatus
  - Track match lifecycle
end note

:Return MatchID List;
note right
  **Output Example**:
  [12345, 67890, 11111, 22222, ...]
  
  **Usage**:
  - Convert to comma-separated string
  - Pass to CTS_MatchInfo_Get SP
  - Get match info from MainDB
  - Update status in CTS database
end note

:Complete;

note right
  **Key Characteristics**:
  
  **Simple SELECT**:
  - No INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE
  - Read-only operation
  - Fast execution
  
  **Used For**:
  - Status synchronization
  - Maintenance job
  - Keep CTS data fresh
  
  **Not Used For**:
  - Classification logic
  - Detection rules
  - Customer tagging
  
  **Performance**:
  - Indexed on EventStatus, IsCompleted
  - DISTINCT to avoid duplicates
  - Ordered for consistency
  
  **Related Tables**:
  - CTSMatchMonitor (main)
  - CTSMatchMonitorDetail (referenced)
end note

stop

@enduml

